                </a></li></ul></div><p><strong>Figure 10.  <span>Granger causality analysis between IC-F and IC-RS for the crossmodal task.</span></strong></p><a id="article1.body1.sec2.sec3.fig3.caption1.p1" name="article1.body1.sec2.sec3.fig3.caption1.p1"></a><p>Post hoc (Tukey HSD) test shows that in the theta band the bottom-up connectivity in the period of 100~200 ms is significantly stronger than that in the baseline (âˆ’100~0 ms). <em>Top-down</em>: Granger causality from IC-F to IC-RS; <em>Bottom-up</em>: Granger causality from IC-RS to IC-F.</p>
